    dc:description "Fig. 22. Paragattendorfia sphaeroides Weyer, 1972, from the Oberrödinghausen railway cutting, (Vöhringer Coll.), holotype GPIT-PV-63909 from bed 3c. Scale bar units =1 mm." ;
